comments: Hart (POR) moves laterall into Bancharo's (ORL) path and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.  Bancharo reflexively places his hand to Hart's back after the initial contact.
Nurkic (POR) steps over the plane of the lane line and remains there prior to Banchero (ORL) releasing his free throw attempt.
Banchero (ORL) avoids making contact with Lillard (POR) as he contests the driving shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Banchero (ORL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Grant (POR) does not establish a legal guarding position in Banchero's path prior to contact occurring during the driving shot attempt.
Harris (ORL) makes body contact with Lillard (POR) that affects his SQBR during the drive. The contact occurs prior to Lillard's normal upward shooting motion.
Carter Jr. (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Harris (ORL) slightly extends his arm before quickly retracting it and marginal arm contact occurs with Lillard (POR) during the driving shot attempt.
Simons (POR) makes incidental hand on ball contact and dislodges the ball away from Wagner (ORL) prior to incidental arm contact occurring thereafter at the end of the drive.
Nurkic (POR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Carter Jr. (ORL) and Hart (POR) come together in transition, and incidental leg to leg contact occurs.
Harris (ORL) contests the shot and makes lower body contact with an airborne Lillard (POR), affecting his jump shot attempt.
Johnson (POR) commits a take foul on Fultz (ORL).
Carter Jr. (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard Lillard (POR).
Harris (ORL) avoids making body contact with Simons (POR) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
